N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 512.3 - Applicability

State Regulations

This Part shall apply to any provider of service that has
been certified to operate or proposes to operate a PROS program that must be
certified by the Office of Mental Health. Notes
